all you want.

35
00:01:40,308 --> 00:01:42,352
[Denver] Ugh, that asshole.

36
00:01:42,435 --> 00:01:44,145
He could use a punch in the face.

37
00:01:45,814 --> 00:01:46,689
[sighs]

38
00:01:46,773 --> 00:01:50,360
