If class is inherited in North Korea,

68
00:03:41,304 --> 00:03:44,515
in the south,
it's wealth that's inherited.

69
00:03:45,308 --> 00:03:46,434
[inhales deeply]

70
00:03:47,060 --> 00:03:48,436
You curious?

71
00:03:48,519 --> 00:03:51,564
About why an immature kid from
a rich family decided to join us?

72
00:03:52,440 --> 00:03:53,399
I guess.

73
00:03:54,651 --> 00:03:56,527
Everyone has their own story.

74
00:04:01,824 --> 00:04:03,868
[tires screeching]

75
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:05,828
[engine revving]

76
00:04:05,912 --> 00:04:06,746
[gear clunks]

77
00:04:06,829 --> 00:04:08,706
[tires screeching]

78
00:04:11,209 --> 00:04:13,211
[rave music playing]

79
00:04:15,588 --> 00:04:17,507
[people cheering]

80
00:04:20,009 --> 00:04:20,969
[laughing]

81
00:04:21,052 --> 00:04:23,513
[indistinct chatter]

82
